---
title: Glazed Pork Tenderloin with Basmati Rice and Veggie Jumble
description: This Asian-inspired meal packs all the flavour of your restaurant favourites. The only difference? It’s way healthier. Lean pork tenderloin is roasted with soy sauce, honey and a bit of Dijon mustard. Then, it's plated on top of a colourful bed of veggies and hearty rice.
